Why Is the Diode Important?

The diode inside the EV ensures that current flows only in the expected direction during the negative half cycle.

If the charger cannot detect the expected negative response:

Charging Disabled

Possible causes:

Missing diode
Damaged charging cable
CP circuit fault
Vehicle-side failure
